      <guid>https://ageldama.github.io/posts/2026-03mar/2026-03mar13--01-ping/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div style=&#34;position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden;&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;iframe allow=&#34;accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share; fullscreen&#34; loading=&#34;eager&#34; referrerpolicy=&#34;strict-origin-when-cross-origin&#34; src=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/embed/oMfMUfgjiLg?autoplay=0&amp;amp;controls=1&amp;amp;end=0&amp;amp;loop=0&amp;amp;mute=0&amp;amp;start=0&#34; style=&#34;position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border:0;&#34; title=&#34;YouTube video&#34;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;…“섬광의 하사웨이”인가 건담극장판에 사용했다고 뜨더라.&#xA;ㅎㅎㅎ그은담아재들이랑 건샌로지스랑 세대가 겹치긴 할거 같다. 🪪&lt;/p&gt;</description>
